title: Bill and Ted 3 casting news!
body:
Amy Stoch (left) returns as Missy.

Beck Bennett (center) will be Deacon Logan (Ted’s younger brother).

Hal Landon, Jr. (right) returns as Ted’s father, Chet Logan (and maybe Abe Lincoln).

Jayma Mays (left) will play Bill’s wife, Princess Joanna.

Erinn Hayes (right) will play Ted’s wife, Princess Elizabeth.

Anthony Carrigan will play the film’s villain.

Samara Weaving (left) will play Bill’s daughter, Thea.

Brigette Lundy-Paine (right) will play Ted’s daughter, Billie.

William Sadler (”Death”) will also return. Dean Parisot (“Galaxy Quest”) will direct from a script by original creators Chris Matheson and Ed Solomon.

summary: Hello love, I was wondering if you could do a dating Bill/Ted headcannon? Thank you! Btw I love your writing ❤️
question: Hello love, I was wondering if you could do a dating Bill/Ted headcannon? Thank you! Btw I love your writing ❤️
answer:
Of course! You’re so sweet. 

(i thought they were boyfriends when i was like, nine)

▁

Dating Bill:

▸ when he asked you out he called you a ‘righteous babe’ 

▸ “we should like, totally make out right now, dude.”

▸ impulsive dates

▸ randomly shows up at your house with like, pizza and says lets watch a movie

▸ always talks about you to his friends, ted especially

▸ confident asf

▸ introduces you as “my lady/dude”

▸ you guys don’t fight at all

▸ you did once, but he got hella sad and apologized immediately 

▸ when he met your parents he called them dude and dudette 

▸ “whats up creators of my babe/dude?”

▸ super supportive in everything you do

▁

Dating Ted:

▸ super understanding 

▸ did air guitar after you said yes to going on a date with him

▸ gets hella nervous on dates

▸ said ‘woah’ after you guys kissed for the first time

▸ opens the door for you

▸ sends you memes at like 3 am

▸ it’s always the love memes

▸ plays guitar for you

▸ you guys eat mountains of food together 

▸ “youre like, beautiful, man”

▸ shy shy shy 

▸ respectful af when meeting your parents 

▸ he still calls them both dude though

▸ respectfully though

▸ he loves to cuddle tbh
